data.title: Vintage Photo Album for Education Infographics
data.meta_description: Remember those old photo albums every grandparents had at home? How about some vintage-looking infographics for Google Slides & PPT?
data.text:
Free Google Slides theme, PowerPoint template, and Canva presentation template

We had a template that was a true vintage photo album, and it was intended for any kind of slideshow for topics related to education. We liked that design so much we've decided to create these supplemental infographics. This means the tables, graphs, diagrams, timelines and percentage gauges have a style that fits to perfection with that template. That includes the typography and the filter applied to the photos (yes, some of these designs come with photos to reinforce that "vintage" look).

Features of these infographics

100% editable and easy to modify

32 different infographics to boost your presentations

Include icons and Flaticon’s extension for further customization

Designed to be used in Google Slides, Canva, and Microsoft PowerPoint and Keynote

16:9 widescreen format suitable for all types of screens

Include information about how to edit and customize your infographics

Supplemental infographics for the template Vintage Photo Album for Education
